These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: zinnia, amaryllis, daisy, begonia, sunflower, balloon-flower, bellflower
There are 7 different favourite beverages: mirinda, coffee, almond-milk, juice, soy-milk, milk, iced-tea
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person who growsdaisy##8
 3. the person drinking mirinda is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 4. the person drinking coffee is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 5. the person who growszinnia is not to the left of the person drinking milk##8
 6. the person who growszinnia is not the person drinking coffee##6
 7. the person who growssunflower is in an odd position##4
 8. the person who growssunflower is not to the left of the person who growsbellflower##8
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking coffee##7
10. the person drinking coffee is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
11. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an odd position##4
12. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
14. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking mirinda##7
15. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
16. the person drinking milk is not to the left of the person who growssunflower##8
17. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
18. the person who growsbellflower is the person drinking almond-milk##1
19. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
20. the person who growsbegonia is not the person drinking milk##6
21. the person who growszinnia is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
22. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |      3       |    4    |    5     |      6      |    7    |
| Flower           | balloon-flower | daisy | bellflower | amaryllis  | sunflower  | begonia | zinnia    |
| Beverage   | coffee   | mirinda   | almond-milk   | juice | soy-milk | iced-tea        | milk |

