 3. the palace house is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1
 4. the vegafina-smoker is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 5. the art-deco house is on the right of the palace house##1
 6. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 7. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5
 8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3
 9. the palace house is in the middle##1
